title: Killest Breakz-Drum n Bass-Dubstep
description:
MASSIVELY UPDATED VERSION SOON!!!

The dopest, killest breakbeats, drum n bass, and dubstep with a few assorted breakcore/glitch/ragga goodies along the way. 

Consider it the personal "best of my harddrive", a gift from me to you.

All files are in MP3 format, all but a few are super high-quality 320 kbps CBR.

Not a joke. Not a virus. Please seed.
